        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Offshore Wind Jobs and Opportunity Act</b></p> <p>This bill authorizes the Department of Energy to award offshore wind career training grants to institutions of higher education or labor organizations to develop, offer, or improve educational or career training programs that provide skills necessary for employment in the offshore wind industry.</p>]]>
        </text>
